OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC News channel fault
OL,4,Cdisrupts start of World Cup preview
OL,5,Cprogramme
OL,6,
OL,7,FA technical issue on the UK BBC News
OL,8,Fchannel caused viewers to miss the
OL,9,Fstart of a World Cup preview programme.
OL,11,FThe programme ` also available as a
OL,12,Flive stream ` was due to start at
OL,13,Faround 5.30pm on the TV news channel.
OL,14,FBut viewers there saw a screen showing
OL,15,Ffour video feeds, in silence.
OL,17,FTwo of the feeds seemed to show
OL,18,FArgentina and England fans making their
OL,19,Fway to the World Cup match in Atlanta,
OL,20,FGeorgia, USA.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,143,140,200,120,0,100
