OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F142A1784256087
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/2
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCBBC News channel fault
OL,4,Cdisrupts start of World Cup preview
OL,5,Cprogramme
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe third feed was mostly blank, apart
OL,8,Ffrom a Press Association logo. And the
OL,9,Ffourth screen showed the schedule of
OL,10,Fevents planned on the Eurovision News
OL,11,FEBU Line 3.
OL,13,FAfter about two minutes of this, the
OL,14,Ftext-based BBC News filler newsSUS was
OL,15,Fput to air.
OL,17,FA little over 35 seconds later, the
OL,18,FWorld Cup preview programme finally
OL,19,Fappeared.
